headline: Why Uber (UBER) Shares Are Sliding Today
summary: Shares of ride sharing and on-demand delivery platform Uber (NYSE:UBER) fell 3.4% in the afternoon session after the company faced mounting regulatory pressure in Europe and a price target reduction from Morgan Stanley. headline: Has Uber’s 243% Three Year Surge Left Further Upside For Investors In 2025
summary: Wondering if Uber Technologies is still worth buying after its huge run, or if the easy money has already been made?
